    <a href="../events.html#lisa99">LISA 1999</a>,
    <a href="mailto:beck@@openbsd.org">Bob Beck</a>.<br>
    <a href="../papers/authgw-paper.ps">я│я┌п╟я┌я▄я▐</a> п╦
    <a href="../papers/authgw-slides.ps">я│п╩п╟п╧п╢я▀</a>.
<p>
<li>Encrypting Virtual Memory<br>
    <a href="../events.html#sec2000">Usenix Security 2000</a>,
    <a href="mailto:provos@@openbsd.org">Niels Provos</a>.<br>
    <a href="../papers/swapencrypt.ps">я│я┌п╟я┌я▄я▐</a> п╦
    <a href="../papers/swapencrypt-slides.ps">я│п╩п╟п╧п╢я▀</a>.
<p>
</ul>

